      <p>&nbsp;</p> 
      <p><strong>Virtual Campus of University of Colombo (VCUC)</strong>&nbsp;that has already been approved by the Council on 09.09.2009 as the campus which delivers courses/ parts of courses utilizing modern open and distance education modes. This centre was made the administrative unit to handle all matters relating external degree programmes and extension courses with the approval of Senate at its meeting on the 28th Virtual Campus of University of Colombo-Coordinating Centre (VCUC-CC).</p> 
